	edit\, debit or mobile pay (such as Apple Pay or Google Pay). Will call ti
	ckets can be picked up on day of show at the Box Office. Box Office opens 
	1 hour prior to door times. You will need a valid photo ID and the credit 
	card used for purchase. ADA tickets can be purchased online - you do not n
	eed to call the box office to place an order. Look for the logo on the Fin
